about a lie.

159
00:08:02,849 --> 00:08:05,613
Sometimes you gotta tell one
until you come up
with something better.

160
00:08:05,685 --> 00:08:07,243
I'll see you soon.

161
00:08:07,320 --> 00:08:08,787
Where you going?
TOMMY: School.

162
00:08:08,855 --> 00:08:11,119
Stay with Mom.
Don't let her
out of your sight.

163
00:08:11,190 --> 00:08:13,385
Can't Sean do that?
Can't Sean do what?

164
00:08:13,459 --> 00:08:14,653
Sean just got out
of the hospital.

165
00:08:14,727 --> 00:08:15,921
Well, he looks okay to me.

166
00:08:15,995 --> 00:08:17,394
Hey, I'm right here.

167
00:08:17,463 --> 00:08:18,452
What are you guys
talking about?

168
00:08:18,531 --> 00:08:21,159
