gotta be losers.

182
00:08:51,564 --> 00:08:52,792
Probably more.

183
00:08:52,865 --> 00:08:55,163
Too bad Louie's not around
to collect.

184
00:08:55,635 --> 00:08:57,102
Get Kevin down here.

185
00:08:57,203 --> 00:08:59,034
Let's figure this thing out.

186
