again last night.

220
00:11:22,481 --> 00:11:24,142
With someone else.

221
00:11:24,850 --> 00:11:26,647
And you feel bad
about that?

222
00:11:26,719 --> 00:11:28,619
Yes.
Good, you should.

223
00:11:30,456 --> 00:11:32,890
What's worse,
I did it to hurt the person

224
00:11:32,958 --> 00:11:34,516
