225
00:11:35,761 --> 00:11:37,456
Who was the first guy.

226
00:11:37,530 --> 00:11:39,327
Who isn't your husband?

227
00:11:41,934 --> 00:11:42,923
No.

228
00:11:45,371 --> 00:11:47,669
