on my calendar.

232
00:12:05,958 --> 00:12:09,450
The day my husband
never came home.

233
00:12:12,431 --> 00:12:14,763
Well, thank God
for small favors.

234
00:12:17,970 --> 00:12:19,631
Your husband was a louse.

235
00:12:20,539 --> 00:12:24,031
